rComments: She cares for her students and wants to learn their names. She tends to call students out in class which is very annoying. She is a hard grader and her instructions for assignments are never clear. She puts comments on your papers saying that you are missing certain things, but those elements were not stated in the instructions.

Mireille is the kindest prof ive had. She cares about her students and tries to suit everyone. Class is videos, group discussion, 3 small papers to do and quiz on readings. Readings gets heavy but it's really easy to pass.

Mireille est vraiment gentille et ses cours sont plaisants à assister! Elle connaît et aime sa matière. Elle est différente des autres profs dans son approche. Les power points et les attentes pour les travaux sont un brin pas assez clair par contre! Je la reprendrais sans hésiter
Une des meilleures prof que j'ai eu depuis mes 3 ans à l'Université. Passionné et très claire dans ces attentes aux travaux, quiz et examens. Définitivement recommender!
Elle est superbe, vraiment bon prof
Une enseignante passionnée par sa matière et très intéressante!

Great prof, always there to help students understand what we covered in class. She uses plenty of different teaching methods; videos, class discussions...Make sure to read all the material because there is a mini test question on almost every one. I recommend this class!
She has a wide range of teaching techniques which can suit anybody. Videos, discussions, games...Variety! Un cours super interessant!
